{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_09_03",
  "title": "神崎莉央",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "教えて。悩んでることが成長って……どういうこと？\nうじうじ悩んでる、私のどこが成長してるっていうのよ",
      "startTime": 5.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 9.8619271915
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。以前の莉央さんなら、こんな風に\n他人と自分の間で悩んだりはしなかったでしょう",
      "startTime": 13.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "自信を持って\n自分の意見を通そうとしたんじゃないでしょうか",
      "startTime": 18.8333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 21.9306794485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、LizNoirのスタイルはそうやって作って\n守ってきた。それが私達の強さだと思ってた",
      "startTime": 25.466666158,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今はそれだけじゃダメだと思うの",
      "startTime": 30.111677456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.5308156809
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "愛やこころを受け入れた時のように\n今までは思いもしなかった意見も取り入れようって",
      "startTime": 36.3333328247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "そう思ってたんだけど……\nそれが正しいのかどうかも分からなくなってきてる",
      "startTime": 42.6666653951,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.1561889173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "ダメね。ブレているのよ、今の私は\nこれじゃ、我を通すだけだった以前の私の方がマシよ",
      "startTime": 51.0333320618,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 54.9978018285
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、我を通すのは強さでもあるけど\n弱さでもあります",
      "startTime": 58.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "どこに弱さがあるっていうの？",
      "startTime": 60.4014526051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 62.7697741113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それは、自分の枠から出ることが出来ない\n臆病さの裏返しでもあるからです",
      "startTime": 65.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "だから今の莉央さんは成長の途中。俺はそう思ってます",
      "startTime": 68.6593865635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 74.3341464283
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "成長の途中、か。そんな風に考えたこと、なかったわ",
      "startTime": 74.3341464283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 81.1804726524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "今の私達に、勢いも実力も備わっているのは確かよ\nでもBIG4にはあと一歩、届かない",
      "startTime": 86.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 90.5936664504
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4入りするためにもっと強くなりたい。勝ちたい",
      "startTime": 90.5936664504,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "そのためにはどうすればいいのか、ずっと考えてる\n……このままじゃ、終われないの",
      "startTime": 100.4999913532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.4101450205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、いつもなら断ってもおかしくない仕事にも\n挑戦しようと思ったんですか？　莉央さんらしいです",
      "startTime": 106.6666534422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう、これから私達はどうすればいいのか\nこのところ、ずっと迷っていたけど……",
      "startTime": 115.5333201089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 118.1499642293
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今の言葉で手がかりが掴めた気がする\n私達はもっと成長出来るはず。……いえ、してみせるわ",
      "startTime": 123.0666534422,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 128.5466524999
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺も他の仕事を調整して\n出来るだけ撮影現場に顔を出すようにします",
      "startTime": 130.7333190916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "いいわよ、無理しなくても\n貴方が見るべきアイドルは、他にも沢山いるんだから",
      "startTime": 135.9999857583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、今がリズノワの正念場なんですよね\n必ず行きますから",
      "startTime": 143.5999857583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 145.3267203092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、期待せずに待ってるわ",
      "startTime": 145.3267203092,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3923.9982605000137,
          "startTime": 149.2507185697
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4257.33159379999,
          "startTime": 149.584051903
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.0007185697
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.0007185697
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……し、失礼します！　撮影は……！？\n……誰もいない。プールの方か？",
      "startTime": 156.166660563,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_spa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5594.919816700013,
          "startTime": 161.7615803797
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.5115803797
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.5115803797
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "撮影は無事に終わったわよ\n……貴方、本当に来たのね",
      "startTime": 165.566660563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……それなら良かった、です……\nでも……遅かったか",
      "startTime": 174.6999999998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio017.m4a",
      "text": "まったくもう……\nそんなにまた、私の水着姿が見たかったの？",
      "startTime": 180.2666646319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違いますよ！　いや、それはそれで失礼か……\nどう答えれば……？",
      "startTime": 188.6999979653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-rio018.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、冗談よ。貴方の顔を見たら\nついホッとして、軽口が出ちゃったわ",
      "startTime": 195.0666646319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_bigpool-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bigpool-00-noon",
      "startTime": 199.0816784619
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_09_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "……その様子だと、いい仕事が出来たみたいですね",
      "startTime": 200.1483380078,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
